title: AHS Complete Timeline: 1500s - 2024 ALL SEASONS!
author: Think Story
comment: Phew, this video took me FOREVER! Would love if you tossed it a like ;) Couldn't include everything but did my best.
Season 8 just tore the timeline in two with all that time traveling

It kinda blows my mind in some way that the events of 2 seasons were happening simultaneously😂 This kinda made the entire show seem so much more cooler!

Thankyou! I'd love an updated version after 10 seasons have aired!
Would have been better if it was narrated, but good job
i never knew Dandy owned the Roanoke house!?!
description:
In this video I pinpoint all of the major events from every season of American Horror Story starting from the 1500s to 2024. This includes up to Season 8 Apocalypse.
